A divinely appointed prophet from the womb:

 Jeremiah 1:5 &#8211; &#8216;Before I formed you in the womb I knew you,
 before you were born I set you apart;
 I appointed you as a prophet to the nations.&#8221;

 Psalm 139:13 &#8211; &#8216;For you created my inmost being;
 you knit me together in my mother&#8217;s womb.&#8217;

 Of course, the question here is: What divine insight does the pro-abortion crowd think they have to where they can destroy in a mother&#8217;s womb that which God is somehow instrumental in creating? (righterreport.com)

 Stop the infanticide of abortion.
